description: Steps to Castle Island and the beaches! One bedroom and one study condo in an victorian brick building with hardwood floors and wood burning fireplace in the living area, large bedroom with extra closet space and a recently renovated tile bath. This unit has lots of character and 10 ft ceilings throughout.  Access to beautiful garden and patio and an extra large shared roof deck with amazing views of the waterfront!
